{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":9000,"text":"I was afraid of womanhood."},{"time":12000,"text":"Not that I'm not afraid now,"},{"time":14000,"text":"but I've learned to pretend."},{"time":16000,"text":"I've learned to be flexible."},{"time":18000,"text":"In fact, I've developed some interesting tools"},{"time":20000,"text":"to help me deal with this fear."},{"time":22000,"text":"Let me explain."},{"time":24000,"text":"Back in the '50s and '60s, when I was growing up,"},{"time":26000,"text":"little girls were supposed to be kind and thoughtful"},{"time":28000,"text":"and pretty and gentle and soft,"},{"time":31000,"text":"and we were supposed to fit into roles"},{"time":33000,"text":"that were sort of shadowy --"},{"time":35000,"text":"really not quite clear what we were supposed to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":41000,"text":"There were plenty of role models all around us."},{"time":43000,"text":"We had our mothers, our aunts, our cousins, our sisters,"},{"time":46000,"text":"and of course, the ever-present media"},{"time":48000,"text":"bombarding us with images and words,"},{"time":51000,"text":"telling us how to be."},{"time":54000,"text":"Now my mother was different."},{"time":56000,"text":"She was a homemaker,"},{"time":58000,"text":"but she and I didn't go out and do girlie things together,"},{"time":60000,"text":"and she didn't buy me pink outfits."},{"time":62000,"text":"Instead, she knew what I needed, and she bought me a book of cartoons."},{"time":65000,"text":"And I just ate it up."},{"time":67000,"text":"I drew, and I drew,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and since I knew that humor was acceptable in my family,"},{"time":72000,"text":"I could draw, do what I wanted to do,"},{"time":74000,"text":"and not have to perform, not have to speak --"},{"time":76000,"text":"I was very shy --"},{"time":78000,"text":"and I could still get approval."},{"time":81000,"text":"I was launched as a cartoonist."},{"time":85000,"text":"Now when we're young,"},{"time":87000,"text":"we don't always know. We know there are rules out there,"},{"time":90000,"text":"but we don't always know --"},{"time":92000,"text":"we don't perform them right,"},{"time":94000,"text":"even though we are imprinted at birth"},{"time":96000,"text":"with these things,"},{"time":99000,"text":"and we're told"},{"time":101000,"text":"what the most important color in the world is."},{"time":104000,"text":"We're told what shape we're supposed to be in."},{"time":107000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":110000,"text":"We're told what to wear --"},{"time":112000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":114000,"text":"-- and how to do our hair --"},{"time":116000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":121000,"text":"-- and how to behave."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124000,"text":"Now the rules that I'm talking about"},{"time":126000,"text":"are constantly being monitored by the culture."},{"time":128000,"text":"We're being corrected,"},{"time":130000,"text":"and the primary policemen are women,"},{"time":133000,"text":"because we are the carriers of the tradition."},{"time":135000,"text":"We pass it down from generation to generation."},{"time":139000,"text":"Not only that --"},{"time":141000,"text":"we always have this vague notion"},{"time":143000,"text":"that something's expected of us."},{"time":145000,"text":"And on top of all off these rules,"},{"time":148000,"text":"they keep changing."},{"time":150000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":154000,"text":"We don't know what's going on half the time,"},{"time":157000,"text":"so it puts us in a very tenuous position."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162000,"text":"Now if you don't like these rules,"},{"time":164000,"text":"and many of us don't --"},{"time":166000,"text":"I know I didn't, and I still don't,"},{"time":169000,"text":"even though I follow them half the time,"},{"time":171000,"text":"not quite aware that I'm following them --"},{"time":173000,"text":"what better way than to change them [than] with humor?"},{"time":178000,"text":"Humor relies on the traditions of a society."},{"time":181000,"text":"It takes what we know, and it twists it."},{"time":184000,"text":"It takes the codes of behavior and the codes of dress,"},{"time":186000,"text":"and it makes it unexpected,"},{"time":188000,"text":"and that's what elicits a laugh."},{"time":190000,"text":"Now what if you put together women and humor?"},{"time":193000,"text":"I think you can get change."},{"time":195000,"text":"Because women are on the ground floor,"},{"time":197000,"text":"and we know the traditions so well,"},{"time":199000,"text":"we can bring a different voice to the table."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201000,"text":"Now I started drawing"},{"time":203000,"text":"in the middle of a lot of chaos."},{"time":205000,"text":"I grew up not far from here in Washington D.C."},{"time":207000,"text":"during the Civil Rights movement, the assassinations,"},{"time":210000,"text":"the Watergate hearings and then the feminist movement,"},{"time":213000,"text":"and I think I was drawing,"},{"time":215000,"text":"trying to figure out what was going on."},{"time":217000,"text":"And then also my family was in chaos,"},{"time":220000,"text":"and I drew to try to bring my family together --"},{"time":223000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":228000,"text":"-- try to bring my family together with laughter."},{"time":231000,"text":"It didn't work."},{"time":233000,"text":"My parents got divorced, and my sister was arrested."},{"time":236000,"text":"But I found my place."},{"time":238000,"text":"I found that I didn't have to wear high heels,"},{"time":240000,"text":"I didn't have to wear pink,"},{"time":242000,"text":"and I could feel like I fit in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245000,"text":"Now when I was a little older, in my 20s,"},{"time":248000,"text":"I realized there are not many women in cartooning."},{"time":251000,"text":"And I thought, \"Well, maybe I can break"},{"time":253000,"text":"the little glass ceiling of cartooning,\""},{"time":255000,"text":"and so I did. I became a cartoonist."},{"time":257000,"text":"And then I thought -- in my 40s I started thinking,"},{"time":260000,"text":"\"Well, why don't I do something?"},{"time":262000,"text":"I always loved political cartoons,"},{"time":264000,"text":"so why don't I do something with the content of my cartoons"},{"time":267000,"text":"to make people think about the stupid rules that we're following"},{"time":270000,"text":"as well as laugh?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":273000,"text":"Now my perspective"},{"time":275000,"text":"is a particularly --"},{"time":277000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":279000,"text":"-- my perspective is a particularly American perspective."},{"time":281000,"text":"I can't help it. I live here."},{"time":284000,"text":"Even though I've traveled a lot,"},{"time":286000,"text":"I still think like an American woman."},{"time":288000,"text":"But I believe that the rules that I'm talking about"},{"time":290000,"text":"are universal, of course --"},{"time":292000,"text":"that each culture has its different codes of behavior"},{"time":295000,"text":"and dress and traditions,"},{"time":297000,"text":"and each woman has to deal with these same things"},{"time":299000,"text":"that we do here in the U.S."},{"time":301000,"text":"Consequently, we have."},{"time":303000,"text":"Women, because we're on the ground, we know the tradition."},{"time":306000,"text":"We have amazing antennae."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309000,"text":"Now my work lately"},{"time":311000,"text":"has been to collaborate with international cartoonists,"},{"time":313000,"text":"which I so enjoy,"},{"time":316000,"text":"and it's given me a greater appreciation"},{"time":318000,"text":"for the power of cartoons"},{"time":320000,"text":"to get at the truth,"},{"time":324000,"text":"to get at the issues quickly and succinctly."},{"time":327000,"text":"And not only that, it can get to the viewer"},{"time":329000,"text":"through not only the intellect, but through the heart."},{"time":332000,"text":"My work also has allowed me to collaborate"},{"time":335000,"text":"with women cartoonists from across the world --"},{"time":337000,"text":"countries such as Saudi Arabia,"},{"time":339000,"text":"Iran, Turkey,"},{"time":341000,"text":"Argentina, France --"},{"time":343000,"text":"and we have sat together and laughed"},{"time":345000,"text":"and talked and shared our difficulties."},{"time":347000,"text":"And these women are working so hard to get their voices heard"},{"time":350000,"text":"in some very difficult circumstances."},{"time":353000,"text":"But I feel blessed to be able to work with them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357000,"text":"And we talk about"},{"time":359000,"text":"how women have such strong perceptions,"},{"time":361000,"text":"because of our tenuous position"},{"time":363000,"text":"and our role as tradition-keepers,"},{"time":366000,"text":"that we can have the great potential"},{"time":369000,"text":"to be change-agents."},{"time":371000,"text":"And I think, I truly believe,"},{"time":374000,"text":"that we can change this thing"},{"time":376000,"text":"one laugh at a time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}